###GET Purchase orders
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/EPMService/POEntitySet
Authorization: Basic Tarak
###GET Single Purchase order
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/EPMService/POEntitySet/PO002

### Get Count of Purchase orders
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/EPMService/POEntitySet/$count

###Get only certain fields of purchase order
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/EPMService/POEntitySet?$select=NET_Amount,PO_ID,CURRENCY_code

###Get BP having name Reliance Retail Ltd.
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/EPMService/BPEntitySet?$filter=COMPANY_NAME eq 'Reliance Retail Ltd.'

### Get BPs having name contains R in there company name

http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/EPMService/BPEntitySet?$filter=Contains(COMPANY_NAME,'a')

### Get Addressess of BPs
http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/EPMService/BPEntitySet?$select=BP_ID&$expand=Address_Guid

